{"tid":1694331,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"警隊臨床心理學家指警察對示威口號產生幻聽、躁鬱","createTime":"2019-11-05T06:03:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T07:22:56.000Z","uid":222970,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d65d34468830320004522a0149296a43ad15098e","tid":1694331,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T06:03:21.000Z","msg":"［轉載自TG]<br />\n朋友既朋友 警隊臨床心理學家指出唔少警察<br />\n長期聽到針對警察示威口號產生幻聽、躁鬱、最嚴重會患上抑鬱等<br />\n<br />\n若示威者同警察距離非常近既時候, 利用群眾優勢<br />\n不要說「黑警，可恥」, 試著說「黑社會」,這種標籤化令警察內心會感自愧, 壓力倍僧, 行為自動檢點<br />\n<br />\n進一步造成心理創傷口號，不要說「香港警察，知法犯法」<br />\n試著說「不畏懼、不徇私、不對他人懷惡意」此口號出自警察誓言, 當有人不斷叫出此口號，警察會回憶畢業既誓言，開始對自己身份認同產生懷疑同混淆, 精神疲乏, 有部份警察雙眼通紅、帶有淚光<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uGFQJQB.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuGFQJQB.gif&h=73396873&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7yFhoQz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7yFhoQz.jpg&h=ebd8ce3d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zFOnzXi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzFOnzXi.jpg&h=d79e4b60&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f50a9269ad5eba0a55457fca51e6fb24ac6fb1c8","tid":1694331,"uid":235025,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T06:05:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"883df008b8b84f0be80b7c6aecf41cf6d1b876c3","tid":1694331,"uid":31151,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T06:08:30.000Z","msg":"呢篇野好似幾個月前睇過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dabb36c7b4785840f63496d6ac4beceeb6768850","tid":1694331,"uid":199926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T06:09:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fUUmQwH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfUUmQwH.png&h=4f6d902a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n約定你11月6 Sogo崇光百貨感謝